{"tid":2053480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人民日报：追殺韓國瑜 民進黨醜態百出","createTime":"2020-06-06T10:08:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T11:39:04.000Z","uid":277037,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"49a8f91d2cef3b0537635006ba95e1c75dc9a9ff","tid":2053480,"uid":277037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T10:08:49.000Z","msg":"罷韓案要達成罷免目的，同意票數必須大於不同意票，且同意票數須達到高雄市選舉人數的25％，也就是約57萬張同意票。從民調數字看，罷韓結果仍有懸念。親綠《寶島通訊社》5月25日發布&ldquo;高雄市長罷免投票&rdquo;封關民調，結果顯示，有45.5%一定會去投票，25.2%可能會去投票。而國民黨智庫民調顯示，高雄市民對韓國瑜防疫措施，滿意的高達55.8%，不滿意的只有32.6%。對民進黨鼓吹的&ldquo;罷韓&rdquo;贊成的只有27.7%，不贊成的有53.3%。有觀察者認為，罷韓最後差距票數會在3萬票內，若6日高雄下雨，影響投票意願，則韓國瑜有可能&ldquo;<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">逃過一劫</span></span>&rdquo;。<br />\n  韓國瑜市政成績不錯，但民進黨的一貫策略是不問事實只講情緒，一意煽動高雄人對韓國瑜&ldquo;背叛高雄&rdquo;的恨意。島內輿論評論說，罷韓將開啟台灣政治史的惡性循環，也再次凸顯了台灣所謂的&ldquo;民主政治&rdquo;早已淪落為只問顏色不問對錯的&ldquo;顏色政治、私心政治、騙術政治&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n瞓咗無睇，韓國瑜逃過一劫未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7058566a7b1f32e3ac61bf35235505a37c037b6","tid":2053480,"uid":277037,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T10:10:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uEu8UZm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuEu8UZm.jpg&h=463f247b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHJYxL2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHJYxL2.png&h=9ad4b5d1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qrN6GEC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqrN6GEC.gif&h=c758d442&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XN9AzZE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXN9AzZE.gif&h=9679a5aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n慢慢哭喪啦韓粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad9e6382f346037f914fae05a0494a292134ec1","tid":2053480,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T11:32:08.000Z","msg":"你吹得我漲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b602a3c607af2c56fd29f997c47f32b07e9728","tid":2053480,"uid":352936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T11:35:08.000Z","msg":"原來落雨就唔會去投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中共係咪要日日作法"},{"pid":"28831e58f0326ba6d375a94fc4fcaf192db4f5c0","tid":2053480,"uid":105140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T11:37:57.000Z","msg":"追殺民進黨，人民日報醜態百出"},{"pid":"1c520d0a920254ff21a594fe28336f1b573899c9","tid":2053480,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T11:39:04.000Z","msg":"中共最驚就係輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}